OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHalf of Port Talbot Tata   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjobs at risk, unions told  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Half of the workforce at Tata Steel's  
OL,6, plant in Port Talbot are at risk of    
OL,7, redundancy, unions have been told.     
OL,9,FIn total, the company has said 2,423   
OL,10,Fjobs across the UK are at risk, with   
OL,11,F1,929 of those in Port Talbot, which   
OL,12,Femploys 3,859 people.                  
OL,14,FTata presented a breakdown of its      
OL,15,Fproposed restructure to union bosses at
OL,16,Fa meeting in Birmingham on Friday.     
OL,18,FIt said it recognised this was an      
OL,19,F"unsettling" time and that it would    
OL,20,Fsupport all those affected.            
